3. No AI Training or Development

You may not use the Work, in whole or in part, directly or indirectly, as
input, training data, validation data, test data, evaluation data, or reference
data for:

- training, pre-training, fine-tuning, aligning, validating, testing,
  benchmarking, or evaluating an artificial intelligence or machine-learning
  model, system, service, dataset, or technology;
- developing, improving, calibrating, or operating an artificial intelligence
  or machine-learning model, system, service, dataset, or technology; or
- creating embeddings, feature representations, model weights, synthetic
  training data, or other machine-readable representations for any purpose
  described above.

This restriction applies regardless of whether the activity is commercial,
non-commercial, private, academic, or research-oriented.

For clarity, ordinary playback, search indexing that does not train or improve
an AI or machine-learning technology, format conversion, compression, and
audio analysis solely for reproducing, distributing, performing, modifying,
or describing the Work are permitted.

